author: Ryan George Extra Plus!
description:
It always amazes me to see what the wealthiest people end up putting in their homes. Limitless design choices and they still settle on some truly bizarre things. Well, it’s time once again to crack open the door on some of these big dumb luxury homes and see what kind of insane things we can find - spoilers, it gets weird.
